project.name: Rhythm
project.notes: 1. Click on a color dot to hear how does it sound.2. Double click to cloneit.3. Place the clone on the circle.4. Pressthe play button. The Turtle is a DJ. You can programit to create a track with multiple rhythms. You canrecord yours elf, create a dot with your sound and put it on thecircle.
